{"tid":1967073,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣糧食內銷需求暴增，「蔬菜箱」兩個月業績近2億","createTime":"2020-04-10T15:47:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T16:59:03.000Z","uid":11598,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"42a55c1a1687b670a87945c8dee290394819d286","tid":1967073,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T15:47:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HkG3cvujV38\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DHkG3cvujV38&d=PwmYTnxQQ9jzt6ozq479VWXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=c3fdfcd4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HkG3cvujV38</a><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎（2019冠狀病毒疾病，COVID-19）疫情嚴峻，衝擊國產農產品內外銷市場，農委會2月4日起推出「滿500送50」網購促銷方案，40多家電商參與，至3月下旬時業績直逼2億元。中央社記者楊淑閔攝 109年4月3日<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/ahel/202004030125.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fahel%2F202004030125.aspx&d=PwmYTnxQQ9jzt6ozq479VWXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=993a25e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/ahel/202004030125.aspx</a><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎（2019冠狀病毒疾病，COVID-19）疫情嚴峻，全球民眾減少出門消費，國產農產內外銷商機也受挫。因應民眾消費行為改變，農委會國際處2月4日起推出「台灣農產嘉年華-滿500送50」網購促銷活動，提振買氣。<br />\n<br />\n農委會國際處副處長林志鴻告訴中央社記者，這個媒合電商銷售國產農產品的網路促銷活動舉辦到6月底，目標要達到新台幣7億元，統計至3月26日為止，在40多家電商共襄盛舉下，約1個半月多營業額合計已達新台幣1.7億元，直追2億元。<br />\n<br />\n他說，熱銷品項共計4類，包含能在家料理的產品，例如蔬菜箱、冷凍肉及水產；便於保存的產品，例如米、蓬萊麵（國產米製造）及豆奶；補元氣的產品，例如滴雞精；水果。<br />\n<br />\n他強調，受青睞的產品就是方便料理的國產農產品，不論是生鮮蔬菜、肉、水產，或是料理過、加熱就能吃的料理包，都是經過加工處理的，消費者在家能輕鬆烹煮食用，相信促銷結束後仍有不錯的回購率，可培植國產農產拓展網購新商機。<br />\n<br />\n國際處幕僚並說，近期受疫情影響，銷況不好、拍賣價一直偏低的短期葉菜，經初步整理，搭配蔬菜箱包裝，在這次行銷活動中也成為熱銷產品。"},{"pid":"25a1eb7d01737ddb7103c51ebc4e525ac42c317f","tid":1967073,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T15:50:47.000Z","msg":"自給自足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0dfe8084fbe6ecbfa2599afb1f19ce6a986d49b","tid":1967073,"uid":280058,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T15:52:08.000Z","msg":"仲要內銷 自給自足 洗唔洗咁屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28edd5a498c874599c807c94a14041f075aec799","tid":1967073,"uid":237300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0dfe8084fbe6ecbfa2599afb1f19ce6a986d49b","tid":1967073,"uid":280058,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T15:52:08.000Z","msg":"仲要內銷 自給自足 洗唔洗咁屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T15:55:43.000Z","msg":"所以香港可以點樣企穩？"},{"pid":"82aa379413a4c9dd616429a3aa23dae00d00ee95","tid":1967073,"uid":177736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T15:55:55.000Z","msg":"自給自足 幾撚好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bb6203561e9268b51ba70948b11d08d10914aae","tid":1967073,"uid":176282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28edd5a498c874599c807c94a14041f075aec799","tid":1967073,"uid":237300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0dfe8084fbe6ecbfa2599afb1f19ce6a986d49b","tid":1967073,"uid":280058,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T15:52:08.000Z","msg":"仲要內銷 自給自足 洗唔洗咁屈機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T15:55:43.000Z","msg":"所以香港可以點樣企穩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T15:57:33.000Z","msg":"咩產業都冇，就係支那預要食硬香港"},{"pid":"36d670968f0405e6473482ae7b765b390ff996d8","tid":1967073,"uid":334796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T16:59:03.000Z","msg":"糧荒個時 香港就真係仆得街 又會好似口罩禁 俾多多錢人地國家都唔賣俾你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}